July 15th, 1910
Dear Sirs:
Years of study and constant experimenting
have taught us to imitate typewriting so per-
fectly that our letters answer every business
purpose as if written one at a time in your
own office.
You will never know the good work we pro-
duce until you try us with a sample order.
Give us one trial--just one--and then if you
think it to your interest to deal elsewhere,
we shall not have a word to say. We are
anxious to have your circular letter orders,
but want first of all, to deserve them.
We duplicate all styles of typewriter.
If interested in circular letter adver-
tising and nearly every one is- we will
cheerfully give you any other information you
may desire, regarding our process, and we feel
sure if you will try us once you will admit
that we can "make good.
We are prepared to do all kinds of
Printing, Addressing, Folding and Mailing at
reasonable prices.
Yours very truly,
Kriedt Printing and Addressing Co.

July 15th, 1910
Dear Sirs:
Years of study and constant experimenting
have taught us to imitate typewriting so per-
fectly that our letters answer every business
purpose as if written one at a time in your
own office.
You will never know the good work we pro-
duce until you try us with a sample order.
Give us one trial--just one--and then if you
think it to your interest to deal elsewhere,
we shall not have a word to say. We are
anxious to have your circular letter orders,
but want first of all, to deserve them.
We duplicate all styles of typewriter.
If interested in circular letter adver-
tising and nearly every one is- we will
cheerfully give you any other information you
may desire, regarding our process, and we feel
sure if you will try us once you will admit
that we can "make good.
We are prepared to do all kinds of
Printing, Addressing, Folding and Mailing at
reasonable prices.
Yours very truly,
Kriedt Printing and Addressing Co.

July 15th, 1910
Dear Sirs:
Years of study and constant experimenting
have taught us to imitate typewriting so per-
fectly that our letters answer every business
purpose as if written one at a time in your
own office.
You will never know the good work we pro-
duce until you try us with a sample order.
Give us one trial--just one--and then if you
think it to your interest to deal elsewhere,
we shall not have a word to say. We are
anxious to have your circular letter orders,
but want first of all, to deserve them.
We duplicate all styles of typewriter.
If interested in circular letter adver-
tising and nearly every one is- we will
cheerfully give you any other information you
may desire, regarding our process, and we feel
sure if you will try us once you will admit
that we can "make good.
We are prepared to do all kinds of
Printing, Addressing, Folding and Mailing at
reasonable prices.
Yours very truly,
Kriedt Printing and Addressing Co.

July 15th, 1910
Dear Sirs:
Years of study and constant experimenting
have taught us to imitate typewriting so per-
fectly that our letters answer every business
purpose as if written one at a time in your
own office.
You will never know the good work we pro-
duce until you try us with a sample order.
Give us one trial--just one--and then if you
think it to your interest to deal elsewhere,
we shall not have a word to say. We are
anxious to have your circular letter orders,
but want first of all, to deserve them.
We duplicate all styles of typewriter.
If interested in circular letter adver-
tising and nearly every one is- we will
cheerfully give you any other information you
may desire, regarding our process, and we feel
sure if you will try us once you will admit
that we can "make good.
We are prepared to do all kinds of
Printing, Addressing, Folding and Mailing at
reasonable prices.
Yours very truly,
Kriedt Printing and Addressing Co.
